These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, zombie
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, tram
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | zombie |
| Transport     | tram | scooter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, artichoke
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | corn      | artichoke         |
| Sport   | weightlifting | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: onion, plum
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | coffee   |
| Food       | plum  | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican
